Class Agent

  • java.lang.Object
    • sajas.core.Agent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Agent
extends java.lang.Object
implements TimerListener
    This is the base class for implementing agents. Note: this class does not extend jade.core.Agent due to non-public method declarations that needed to be re-implemented.

    hlc
